_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2500&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=deccd5a028354298bf958f6bceb882db 2000w"
                    />

                    
    


    <img
        class=""
        alt=""
        width="2400"
        height="3000"
        loading="lazy" js-autosizes        src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250328-Birks-EdMartin-Sequence-19_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1000&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=3d138b9e6ca8a741eb310f24986f5a71"
